    "causal_summary": "sk-design is a thin design-family umbrella router. It keeps the sibling design skills independently invokable, routes generic design entry prompts to the smallest useful child, and owns only shared base vocabulary for anti-slop critique, design tokens, and cognitive laws. Detailed design judgment, extraction mechanics, motion guidance, foundations guidance, and audit contracts remain child-owned.",
